{"article_id":"EETsYp6cHeAq6xOa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN ) -","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Sens . Joe Manchin , D-West Virginia , and Patrick J. Toomey , R-Pennsylvania , plan to announce a bipartisan deal on background checks for gun shows and Internet sales at an 11 a.m. press conference today ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"CNN 's Dana Bash has learned .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"A Democratic leadership source says","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"the compromise will likely be the first amendment to gun legislation","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"being considered ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"after the Senate votes to begin the gun debate Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"READ MORE :","depth":3},{"id":8,"text":"CNN Poll :","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"Popular background checks also cause worry","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"The breakthrough background check agreement is a key part of gun legislation .","depth":3},{"id":11,"text":"Because it has been struck by two senators with strong support from the NRA ,","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"they hope to find the 60 votes","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"that will be needed","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"to overcome opposition","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"to pass their amendment","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The senate is expected to debate gun legislation for at least two weeks .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"Democrats believe","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"as many as a dozen GOP senators will vote with them ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"making up for the handful of pro-gun Democrats","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"who might vote against beginning debate on the bill .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Fourteen Republicans promise to filibuster","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"taking up the measure .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Several Republican senators told CNN Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"they would only vote to begin debate on the bill","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"if they were assured by Democrats","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"they would be allowed to offer amendments to the legislation .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Democratic leaders want to give senators from both parties ample opportunities","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"to amend the bill","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"and are prepared to debate it beyond a scheduled recess the first week in May ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"if doing so will increase the chances of passage .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"\" The way","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"you put together a coalition","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"to pass the bill","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"is to allow as many amendment votes","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"as you can .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"We are willing to take the time","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to do that","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and have that process , \"","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"the aide said .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Those negotiators will now have more time","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"to find common ground on language ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"since the gun debate is expected to be lengthy .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Democratic leaders also argue","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"any bill","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"they put on the floor","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"will represent a substantial improvement in gun safety .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Many of those additional votes could be politically difficult for centrist Democrats , especially those up for re-election in red states ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"as Republicans are expected to craft amendments","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"designed to put those senators on the spot .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Nevertheless , Democratic leaders have determined","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"it ' s a risk","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"they need to take","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"if they want to pass substantive legislation","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"to respond to the mass shootings","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"that have plagued the nation in recent years .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"\" Once we ' re on it","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"we want to have an open process","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"where there are a lot of votes","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and we really work through that , \"","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"the aide said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":121,"left":70,"right":120,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":67,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":0,"right":66,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":66,"left":62,"right":65,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":64,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":3,"right":63,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":63,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":7,"right":68,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":75,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":10,"right":74,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":11,"right":73,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":12,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":13,"right":71,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":85,"right":118,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":85,"left":16,"right":84,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":80,"right":83,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":78,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":17,"right":77,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":18,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"